name: Alby #Mischief: Red -1,1
description: The 2nd piece in the Alby #Mischief collection.  All Alby Wistar #Mischief pieces will be 1/1.  The mischief collection has no upper limit to number.  The aim of the #Mischief collection is to initiate a plague of "Uniquely Generic" Alby NFTs.  New Alby #Mischief pieces will be minted by Alby Wistar periodically.  Primary purchase of an original #Mischief piece will entitle the buyer to request a customised #Mischief piece to be minted for the collection (DM with @AlbyWistar).
